1. *Vratiti* će mi se novac u naredna tri dana. (The money will be returned to me in the next three days.) 
2. On je odlučio da *vrati* svoju sestru odmah iz škole. (He decided to take his sister home from school right away.)
3. Ona je obećala da će *vratiti* knjigu u knjižaru. (She promised to return the book to the bookstore.)
4. Ona je morala da *vratiti* sebi svoju ljubav. (She had to regain her love.)
5. Oni će *vratiti* sebi svoju slobodu. (They will regain their freedom.)